Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Developers spend hours inside the same work surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.22,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Most themes are either too limited, or they cover the workspace,\Nbreak layout, and add background overhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Codex Dream Skin makes Codex personal without sacrificing\Nreadability, stability, or control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The workflow starts with a visual brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Codex and GPT-5.6 organize color, backgrounds,\Noriginal Image2 mecha-cat variants, semantic icons, and animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Every item has a role, version, release status,\Nand publication boundary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a static wallpaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The theme is split into independent background, character,\Nglass-surface, button, and interaction modules.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:01:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tests and payload budgets run first. Then a local CDP one-shot\Napplies modules without patching the official app.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After activation, native functions remain intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The left navigation uses dimensional,\Nsemantic cat-inspired icons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The background preserves a readable work-safe area.
